data.description: Welcome home.  This lovely 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers  a spacious combination living-dining room equipped with a gas log fireplace The large eat-in kitchen provides plenty of room  for friends to gather.  Separated from the kitchen by a small hallway is the spacious family room and is located at the opposite side of the house from the three bedrooms.  Off the family room is a full bath and laundry area.  The hall bath has been completely redone with walk-in shower.  In the evening you may enjoy sitting in the large screened porch.  Heat pump air conditioning system is less than two years old.  A two car carport will shelter your car from the weather. Outside, the spansive 1.59 acre lawn is level.  A huge barn may be used as a workshop that has a seperatea large storage storage room at the back. An all new septic system has just been installed.   Please call today to schedule an appointment to see this home.
